  <brief_title>Activated Recombinant Human Factor VII in Patients With Dengue Haemorrhagic Fever</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multi-centre, Randomised, Double-blind, Parallel Group, Placebo-controlled Comparison of Recombinant Factor VIIa (NovoSevenÂ®) and Standard Haemostatic Replacement Therapy in Patients With Dengue Haemorrhagic Fever</official_title>
  <sponsors>
