  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This trial is conducted in Asia. The aim of this is to investigate the efficacy and safety of
      activated recombinant human factor VII (rFVIIa) in achieving haemostasis in patients with
      Dengue haemorrhagic fever (DHF).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
